OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The German parliament has passed a law 
OL,6, making it easier for citizens and      
OL,7, residents to legally change gender.    
OL,9,FIt's also introducing hefty fines - in 
OL,10,Fspecific circumstances - for disclosing
OL,11,Fsomeone's prior registered name or     
OL,12,Fgender without consent.                
OL,14,FPreviously, changing your registered   
OL,15,Fgender required a doctor's certificate 
OL,16,Fand the approval of a family court.    
OL,18,FNow over-18s can change to male, female
OL,19,For diverse, a third gender option that 
OL,20,Falready exists under German law.       
